text.section:
As a condition of receiving the governmental funds, the corporation's board of directors shall include the following among its directors:
The Governor or his or her designee;
The Attorney General or his or her designee;
The President of the Senate or his or her designee;
The Speaker of the House or his or her designee;
The secretary of the Cabinet for Health and Family Services or his or her designee; and
The commissioner of the Department of Alcoholic Beverage Control or his or her designee.
